So the disability fair everyone turned out to be a wonderful, wonderful event.

159
00:11:36,430 --> 00:11:39,274
My gosh, talk about all the different vendors.

160
00:11:39,955 --> 00:11:44,321
I mean, first and foremost, kudos goes out to.

161
00:11:46,103 --> 00:11:49,605
The, the custodians at the Brooks, right?

162
00:11:49,645 --> 00:12:02,811
Because I thought we were all going to do the setup together and I walked in and somehow they had set these tables up in a way that I think we had close to 30.

163
00:12:03,771 --> 00:12:05,312
30 participating vendors.

164
00:12:05,352 --> 00:12:07,013
I think a couple didn't show up, but.

165
00:12:08,008 --> 00:12:16,110
definitely over 25 vendors and it became a really wonderful and fruitful networking event.

166
