The master list also contains the contact people and email addresses.

169
00:12:39,515 --> 00:12:45,456
That now becomes like your working template if you want to do something.

170
00:12:47,837 --> 00:12:59,080
But some of the speeches made by people with lived experience, either through being family members or having a direct impact,

171
00:13:00,399 --> 00:13:05,164
or being a support source, very, very moving.

172
00:13:05,945 --> 00:13:08,628
