218
00:17:47,359 --> 00:17:49,480
Because I've seen that people are going to Medford.

219
00:17:49,580 --> 00:17:54,001
She said, I lived in South Boston for the last five years.

220
00:17:54,861 --> 00:17:57,202
And she said, Medford is quieter

221
00:17:58,100 --> 00:17:59,280
and more respectful.

222
00:17:59,800 --> 00:18:02,261
And I think we have to really embrace that.

223
00:18:03,001 --> 00:18:04,621
Like, get on that.

224
00:18:05,261 --> 00:18:08,702
So let's look, of course, Frances, at the disabled.

225
00:18:08,762 --> 00:18:17,763
Let's look at the lower income and embrace it and find out where they want to go, where they feel safe.

226
00:18:18,063 --> 00:18:19,504
Is it the public library?

227
00:18:20,364 --> 00:18:21,964
Is it not the Brooks School?

228
00:18:22,224 --> 00:18:27,785
Is it more of Andrew's area, Andrew's Middle School or whatever that area is?

229
00:18:28,809 --> 00:18:29,529
and embrace it.

230
00:18:29,849 --> 00:18:31,310
I don't know how else to explain it.

231
00:18:32,970 --> 00:18:41,972
